      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that it's a lot, but i've seen some biohacking forums saying that mega-dosing for a short burst is actually a standard way to correct a deficiency quickly without waiting months for it to work. if i only do it for like 10 or 14 days, wouldn't the risk be pretty minimal compared to the benefit of getting my energy back? it seems like a lot of trouble to just wait around feeling like this.",
